## 2) Webapp flow
1. Enter parameters (MSE ML, MSE V, MSE AP, iHR V, Gait Speed, etc.).  
2. The app returns **Triad probability (p_RF)** + **risk band** + **top-5 SHAP** + **surrogate rule** (if matched).  
3. (Optional) Enable *Screening mode* to estimate **PPV/NPV** at your **expected prevalence**.

